875
00:39:35,760 --> 00:39:39,140
 A u stvari bez tih dana

876
00:39:39,140 --> 00:39:40,840
 da ti sebi dozvoliš

877
00:39:40,840 --> 00:39:42,620
 da napuniš te neke baterije,

878
00:39:42,620 --> 00:39:43,900
 teško.

879
00:39:43,900 --> 00:39:45,320
 Da, da.

880
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:47,140
 Istina, baš lijepo.

881
00:39:47,140 --> 00:39:48,980
 Si nam onako dala širu sliku.

882
00:39:48,980 --> 00:39:50,140
 Za mislice.

883
00:39:50,140 --> 00:39:51,700
 Ja onako cijelo vrijeme mislim kao,

884
00:39:51,760 --> 00:39:52,320
 to mi je,

885
00:39:52,320 --> 00:39:54,560
 kad imamo dobre govornice u podcastu,

886
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:54,940
 onda onako,

887
00:39:54,940 --> 00:39:56,480
 čekaj vam da ovo završi,

888
00:39:56,480 --> 00:39:57,580
 da malo promislim o tome.

889
00:39:57,580 --> 00:39:59,160
 Treba mi da ovo sad malo mi sjedne,

890
00:39:59,160 --> 00:40:00,480
