898
00:40:12,720 --> 00:40:13,220
 ovaj podcast.

899
00:40:13,220 --> 00:40:15,000
 Joj, pa to si me trebala unaprijed pitati.

900
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:16,580
 Ne, znaš šta ću ti reći?

901
00:40:16,580 --> 00:40:18,900
 Jako mi je zanimljivo što si spontano

902
00:40:18,900 --> 00:40:21,480
