907
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:31,540
 Tako da smo baš pokrile ovoga

908
00:40:31,540 --> 00:40:33,660
 moj nekakav trenutni.

909
00:40:33,880 --> 00:40:34,620
 Doši lijepo.

910
00:40:34,620 --> 00:40:35,580
 Da, da.

911
00:40:35,580 --> 00:40:37,760
 Ali evo, zahvalila bi na pozivu.

912
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:38,700
 Bilo mi je baš jako lijepo

913
00:40:38,700 --> 00:40:39,700
