923
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:51,560
 a naravno i privatno.

924
00:40:51,560 --> 00:40:53,240
 Slažem se, slažem se, da.

925
00:40:53,240 --> 00:40:55,280
 I spojit ćemo Alana i Marka

926
00:40:55,280 --> 00:40:56,380
