929
00:40:59,180 --> 00:41:00,840
 Da razmijene korisne ideje.

930
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:04,520
 Neke šerane kalendare

931
00:41:04,520 --> 00:41:05,280
 i kak se to...

932
