940
00:41:14,740 --> 00:41:16,320
 djecu na Eho Kids

941
00:41:16,320 --> 00:41:17,760
 i dva sata za kavu.

942
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:18,380
 To je to.

943
00:41:18,380 --> 00:41:19,860
 Mi dolazimo sigurno.

944
00:41:19,860 --> 00:41:21,760
 Hvala ti puno, Ricarda.

945
00:41:21,760 --> 00:41:22,980
 Bilo mi baš onako

946
00:41:22,980 --> 00:41:25,560
