947
00:41:25,560 --> 00:41:26,960
 i onako na zabavu zapravo.

948
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:27,700
 Joj, pa hvala ti.

949
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:28,840
 puno mi je baš bilo

950
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:30,160
